When, in disgrace with Fortune and men's eyes, 
I all alone beweep my outcast state,
And trouble deaf heaven with my bootless cries, 
And look upon myself and curse my fate, 
Wishing me like to one more rich in hope, 
Featured like him, like him with friends possessed, 
Desiring this man's art, and that man's scope,
With what I most enjoy contented least;
Yet in these thoughts myself almost despising,
Haply I think on thee; and then my state,
Like to the lark at break of day arising
From sullen earth, sings hymns at heaven's gate;
For thy sweet love remembered such wealth brings
That then I scorn to change my state with kings.

Okay as you can see I think im gonna go round two with this stupid contraption.  The past few days have been great but extremely odd at the same time.   My mom and I are finally starting to get close again, which makes me really happy!  Two of my good friends are leaving me, one in jan/feb and the other in june/july!  Both for military reasons.  I don't know what to really think about it, i guess b/c it hasent hit me yet that they are leaving.  Right now I dont wanna think about it....I just want to spend what time they have left with them and hope for the best.  Just to let you know I will be here when you get back!  For the one supposedly leaving in jan/feb.....I love you with all my heart even though I probably shouldn't.  Anyways on a good note....ONLY 1 week till i get to go visit my cousin im excited about going to the game YAY~ I just wish the damn holidays were over with Christmas sucks and so does new years, for some reason unknown to me I am always the third wheel to everyone else.  These stupid holidays make me feel so lonely, but I guess i'll just have to suck it up and barrel through one more year!  Well im out             HAPPY HOLIDAYS (yeah uh huh)

Oh yeah I hate this damn cold weather....although once someone told me it was perfect cuddle weather, but we see what good that does me....NONE~ !
